name: Travis Peterson
text: These guys are the best!  Devin, Cody, and JM did an AMAZING job upgrading our service panel, installing a generator transfer switch, and several other improvements!  They are professional, courteous, on-time, knowledgeable, I can go on and on.  I will absolutely use them for all of my electrical needs and will refer them to ANYONE and EVERYONE who asks for a referral.  They get the job done right and do not cut corners.  Thanks guys!

name: Tiffany Nichols
text: My workplace had a problem with our electricity, leaving us in a bad way on the Friday heading into a holiday weekend. Hansen electric was fast to respond, and came out quickly. We were back up and running in no time! We are so grateful to the girl in the office who took the call and to Troy who worked in the hot sun to get us taken care of. Many thanks!

name: Jan Allen
text: Made sure I understood the process. Extremely patient with the client. Thank you

name: B. R. Blount
text: First time using Hansens Electric Service and was extremely pleased.  Andrew was our electrician and did a great job!  He was very knowledgeable and professional, and very nice😊. And the cost was fair! Will definitely use them again if needed👍

name: Melissa Ivory
text: I wanted to be sure to leave a review for Tim. He was on time, knowledgeable, professional and so super helpful. Your company does great work and Tim made the appointment completely painless. Thank you very much!

name: pete gleszer
text:
Really impressed with everything involving Hansen Electric. Friendly office staff and service reps. Adapted to the complex install and multi-step process without extra charges or repricing offer. Very near work area in my home and vacuumed up all dust and debris when complete. Price for work was excellent and well below other estimates I received. This is a case where very best costs less.
Exceeded my expectations. Great customer focus and professional skills.

name: Linda Lofton
text: Thank you all for your superior service.  Jake, you got my porch light and carport light working and I so appreciate everything you did. I have more things for you to do after the holidays. Thanks again.
